{"name": "odoo14-addon-l10n-br-purchase-stock", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-l10n-br-purchase-stock", "version": "14.0.3.2.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-l10n-br-purchase", "odoo14-addon-l10n-br-stock-account", "odoo"], "summary": "Brazilian Localization Purchase Stock", "upload_time": 1728000815}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fl10n--brazil-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/l10n-brazil\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/14.0/l10n_br_purchase_stock\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/l10n-brazil-14-0/l10n-brazil-14-0-l10n_br_purchase_stock\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/l10n-brazil&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-mbcosta: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/mbcosta.png?size=40px\n    :alt: mbcosta\n    :target: https://github.com/mbcosta\n    ```\n  maintainer-renatonlima: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/renatonlima.png?size=40px\n    :alt: renatonlima\n    :target: https://github.com/renatonlima\n    ```\n---\n\n# Brazilian Localization Purchase Stock\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:6b8a3d1ec5a68c3c9dde7b00462bd37b3236e4cf733c65001c6537ce5272020f\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module extends the standard Odoo purchase module for Brazil,\nspecially when selling products with NFe's.\n\nIt deals with the propagation of the fiscal operation and allow the creation\nof Picking and Invoices generated by a Purchase Order.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nThis module depends on:\n\n- l10n_br_purchase\n- l10n_br_stock_account\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration required.\n\n## Changelog\n\n### 12.0.1.0.0 (2020-04-27)\n\n- Split l10n_br_purchase module in two l10n_br_purchase and l10n_br_purchase_stock.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_br_purchase_stock%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Renato Lima \\<<mailto:renato.lima@akretion.com.br>>\n- Magno Costa \\<<mailto:magno.costa@akretion.com.br>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- AKRETION LTDA - www.akretion.com\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-renatonlima }} {{ maintainer-mbcosta }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-brazil](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/14.0/l10n_br_purchase_stock) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models.stock_rule", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2020  Renato Lima - Akretion", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models.stock_rule.StockRule", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models.stock_rule.StockRule._run_buy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "procurements", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models.stock_rule.StockRule._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models.purchase_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models..purchase_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models.purchase_order_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_purchase_stock.models..p